snippet.title: IT'S ONLY THE FIRST NIGHT! | Custom Nights at Freddy's - ep.1
snippet.description:
Today I bring you the gameplay of a game that I created myself, is this sad? No, maybe a little bit... But that's not important! Remember that you too can play CNAF and you can download it from Windows, Linux, Mac and Android I hope you like it!
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Hi everyone I'm Cipherwild, I'm a game developer, a model maker, check out my games
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Lost in the Dark Woods:
https://gamejolt.com/games/lost_in_dark_woods/854248
My GameJolt profile:
https://gamejolt.com/@Cipherwild
My Website:
https://cipherwild.com

Currently Lost in the Dark Woods is in Early Access, a great open-world horror is developing, interesting isn't it?
